## CREDIT & FAILURE HANDLING

### When is a credit consumed?
```
Credit consumed → when first AI question is DELIVERED to candidate
                  NOT on interview creation
                  NOT on plan generation
                  NOT on interview start click

Reason: Plan generation or first question can fail silently.
        Credit only consumed when candidate receives actual value.

Implementation:
  createInterviewAction()   → creates record, generates plan, status = PENDING
  startInterviewAction()    → streams first question, on success:
                               1. consumes credit
                               2. sets status = ACTIVE
```

### Interview status → what candidate sees

| Status | What happened | Credit consumed | /interview/[id] shows |
|--------|--------------|----------------|----------------------|
| PENDING | Created, plan ready, not started | No | Pre-interview config + "Start" button |
| ACTIVE | First question delivered | Yes | Live interview — one question at a time |
| COMPLETED | All turns done | Yes | Full conversation replay + "View Report" CTA |
| FAILED | Server error / timeout | Yes | Partial conversation + error banner + support link |
| CANCELLED | Candidate left deliberately | Yes | Partial conversation + cancelled notice |

### Failed interview — what to show
```
/interview/[id] when status = FAILED:

Banner: "Interview ended at Q4 of 12 — technical error"
Below banner: all turns completed so far as chat bubbles
Activities completed before failure: shown with scores
Activities not completed: not shown
Report: "Report unavailable for this session"
Support: "Contact support" link
Credit policy: if < 3 turns completed → "Credit refund — we'll review within 24h"
               if >= 3 turns completed → credit consumed, no refund
```

### Mid-interview recovery (browser crash / network drop)
```
Candidate refreshes /interview/[id]
  → page.tsx detects status = ACTIVE on server
  → renders ActiveInterviewScreen
  → on mount: calls recoverInterviewAction(interviewId)
  → server returns: last AI question + all previous turns
  → store rebuilt from DB data
  → interview continues from last question
  → no credit impact
```

