### Activity panel opens/closes per type

```
Activity type       → Code editor?  → Editable?  → Textarea?
DEBUGGING           → YES (read)    → NO         → NO  (voice explains)
CODE_CORRECTION     → YES (edit)    → YES         → NO  (voice explains fix)
OUTPUT_PREDICTION   → YES (read)    → NO         → NO  (voice predicts)
RESUME_DEFENCE      → NO            → NO         → NO  (voice only)
PRIORITISATION      → NO            → NO         → YES (structure thoughts)
COMMUNICATION       → NO            → NO         → NO  (voice only)
SYSTEM_DESIGN_MINI  → NO            → NO         → YES (write architecture)
```

